   if `ergoemacs-back-to-indentation' is true (otherwise skip).

From:
  (progn
    (ergoemacs-mode 1))| ; Turn on ergoemacs-mode

To:

 (progn
   |(ergoemacs-mode 1)) ; Turn on ergoemacs-mode


4. Move to the beginning of line

From:
  (progn
    |(ergoemacs-mode 1)) ; Turn on ergoemacs-mode

To:

 (progn
|   (ergoemacs-mode 1)) ; Turn on ergoemacs-mode


